r</li><li>1000Mbps Uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>$5.50/mo [<a href=\"https://billing.hudsonvalleyhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=636\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-10155\"></span><br>\n<strong>*Note:</strong> You must click the blue&nbsp;<strong>\u201c<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Continue</span>\u201d</strong> button&nbsp;at the bottom of the page for your discount to be calculated on some of the discounted plans.<br>\n\u201c<strong>FEB2017</strong>\u201d for <strong>35% off</strong> anything on the <a href=\"https://www.hudsonvalleyhost.com\">HudsonValleyHost</a> site&nbsp;except for dedicated servers, colocation, hybrids, managed services, domains, addons and licenses.</p><p>Accepted payment methods are through PayPal, Credit Cards and Bitcoin. <strong>Servers will be setup within 24 hours</strong> once your payment has been made, given that you don\u2019t trigger any fraud protection measures. <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/75982/Nick\">Nick</a>, the brand manager, and his team strive to provide superior&nbsp;24/7 help desk support along with live chat and he\u2019s indicated that he will be available to personally assist customers as needed so please feel free to send him a message over @ <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/75982/Nick\">LowEndTalk</a>.&nbsp;As usual, we suggest you read the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hudsonvalleyhost.com/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a> before purchasing.</p><div><strong>Host Node:&nbsp;</strong></div><p>\u2013 Mix of Dual E5\u2019s and D Series CPU\u2019s<br>\n\u2013 64GB+ RAM<br>\n\u2013 SSD\u2019s in HW RAID<br>\n\u2013 1Gbps uplink</p><div></div><p>Buffalo, NY, USA \u2013 ColoCrossing<br>\nTest IP: 198.12.127.26<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"http://lg.buf.colocrossing.com/100MB.test\">http://lg.buf.colocrossing.com/100MB.test</a></p><p><strong>Buffalo, New York:</strong><br>\n\u2013 270,490 square foot gross; 23,000 square feet of datacenter spac